Package com.b2international.snowowl.api.codesystem.domain

Contains domain model objects related to code system metadata.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ICodeSystem
    Captures metadata about a code system, which holds a set of real-world concepts of medical significance (optionally along with different components forming a description of said concepts) and their corresponding unique code.
    ICodeSystemVersion
    Encapsulates information about released and pending code system versions of a code system.
    ICodeSystemVersionProperties
    Base properties of a code system version.
